segments.text: How are Zina's new programmers working out ?
segments.speaker: S1

segments.text: I hate to admit it , but they're good . And fast . The Filipino kid is a genius .
segments.speaker: S2

segments.text: So you'll make the Stars.com deadline , and have us up and running next week ?
segments.speaker: S1

segments.text: It'll be close , but we'll make it .
segments.speaker: S2

segments.text: Good . After Stars.com starts paying us , we won't need Vikam's cash anymore .
segments.speaker: S1

segments.text: And if we don't need them , we won't need Zina , either .
segments.speaker: S2
